<%- include('partials/header', { currentPage: 'help', title: 'Fix Your Account - Help Center' }) %>

<style>
    body {
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f8fafc, #f1f5f9);
    }
    .help-card {
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .help-card:hover {
        transform: translateX(10px);
        border-color: #7f97d9;
        background-color: #fcfdff;
    }
</style>

<main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="mb-12">
        <nav class="flex mb-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">
            <a href="/dashboard/siswa/help-siswa" class="hover:text-[#7f97d9]">Help Center</a>
            <span class="mx-2">/</span>
            <span class="text-slate-600">Fix Your Account</span>
        </nav>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-slate-800 mb-2">Fix Your Account</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium">Is there any problem with your account access?</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">

        <div class="help-card bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-[2rem] p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 flex-shrink-0 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden p-4">
                <img src="/images/loginfailure.png" alt="Login Failure" class="w-full h-full object-contain" onerror="this.src='https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/6167/6167023.png'">
            </div>
            <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-[#4a6fdc] mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight">Login Failure</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                    Kesulitan masuk ke akun Anda? Pastikan kredensial sudah benar atau periksa apakah koneksi internet Anda stabil. Cobalah hapus cache browser Anda atau gunakan mode incognito.
                </p>
                <button class="mt-4 text-xs font-bold text-[#7f97d9] uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline">Read Troubleshooting →</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="help-card bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-[2rem] p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 flex-shrink-0 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden p-4">
                <img src="/images/acclock.png" alt="Account Locked" class="w-full h-full object-contain" onerror="this.src='https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2889/2889676.png'">
            </div>
            <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-[#4a6fdc] mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight">Account Locked</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                    Akun terkunci biasanya terjadi karena terlalu banyak percobaan login yang salah. Tunggu selama 30 menit atau hubungi admin sekolah melalui email dukungan kami untuk pembukaan akses.
                </p>
                <button class="mt-4 text-xs font-bold text-[#7f97d9] uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline">Request Unlock →</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="help-card bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-[2rem] p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 flex-shrink-0 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden p-4">
                <img src="/images/can'tupdate.png" alt="Can't Update" class="w-full h-full object-contain" onerror="this.src='https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2546/2546743.png'">
            </div>
            <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-[#4a6fdc] mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight">Can't Update Profile</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                    Gagal memperbarui informasi siswa? Pastikan semua format file adalah pdf dan ukuran file tidak melebihi 2MB. Cek kembali kolom wajib yang belum terisi.
                </p>
                <button class="mt-4 text-xs font-bold text-[#7f97d9] uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline">View File Standards →</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="help-card bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-[2rem] p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 flex-shrink-0 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden p-4">
                <img src="/images/forgetpass.png" alt="Forget Password" class="w-full h-full object-contain" onerror="this.src='https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/6195/6195700.png'">
            </div>
            <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-[#4a6fdc] mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight">Forget Password</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                    Lupa kata sandi? Gunakan fitur "Forgot Password" pada halaman login. Sistem akan mengirimkan instruksi pemulihan ke email siswa yang terdaftar di database kami.
                </p>
                <button class="mt-4 text-xs font-bold text-[#7f97d9] uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline">Reset Password Now →</button>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>